agino Sans GB W3&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">已发表论文140余篇，培养博士和硕士研究生19名。主编《临床肿瘤学概论》、《恶性淋巴瘤》等6部专著。先后获得上海市医学和国家教委科技进步二等奖和三等奖各二项。</span></p>','朱雄增教授',NULL,'../UpLoadFiles/LectureImg/20170331122600.PNG','2017-04-01 19:30:23','2017-04-01 19:30:30','24','1','复旦大学附属肿瘤医院病理科教授，博士生导师，长期从事病理诊断和研究工作，有丰富的病理诊断经验。','http://www.91360.com/201509/23/7584.html','../UpLoadFiles/LectureImg/20170331123814.PNG','1','0','','复旦大学附属肿瘤医院朱雄增教授为大家带来“淋巴瘤病理诊断基础”。','淋巴瘤病理诊断,朱雄增,淋巴瘤误诊','2',''), ('14','霍奇金淋巴瘤病理诊断及体会','<p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 150%; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://super.91360.com/ueditor/net/upload/image/20170328/6362630891740030398481778.jpg\" title=\"12.jpg\" alt=\"12.jpg\"/></span></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\">翟琼莉</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">: 女</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">，主任医师</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">天津医科大学肿瘤</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">医院病理科淋巴瘤病理专业</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">组</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">组长</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从事临床病理诊断工作</span>20余年，具有丰富的病理诊断经验，</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">擅长</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">淋巴造血系统肿瘤，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">头颈部及脑系肿瘤的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">病理诊断，并曾多次受邀在全国病理高峰论坛会议上发言。近年来，为提高基层医院病理科淋巴肿瘤的诊断水平，多次在网络平台进行淋巴瘤诊断知识讲座，并建立微信公众号（轻松诊断</span>086），将自己的淋巴瘤诊断经验定期更新，以使更多的低年资病理医生受益。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\">社会任职</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\">：</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国抗癌协会肿瘤转移专委会委员</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国抗癌协会血液学分会病理学组委员</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中国病理学工作者委员会</span>(CCP)淋巴瘤学组成员</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天津市抗癌协会血液肿瘤专委会委员</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">教育工作</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经历：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">1999年毕业于天津医科大学获病理学硕士学位</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">2002年毕业于中国协和医科大学获病理学与病</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生理学博士学位</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">2004年1月-2006.</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">4</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在法国巴黎圣路易医院做博士后研究员</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">2010.2-2010.8被派往美国内布拉斯加大学医学中心研修淋巴造血肿瘤病理</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">1990.8-</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">200</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">8</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">.2</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">河北省保定市第三医院病理科</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">工作，</span>2002年破格晋升副主任医师，2006年破格晋升主任医师，任科</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主任</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">6年</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">2008年3月</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">-至今作为</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">天津医科大学肿瘤</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">医院引进人才调入病理科</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">工作</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">任</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">淋巴瘤病理专业</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">组长</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px;line-height:150%\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学术</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">成果：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">自</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\">1999年以来</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，一直从事造血干细胞和白血病肿瘤干细胞生物学特性相关的研究工作</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，先后在国内外学术期刊发表了多篇论著</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。博士研究生期间</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family: