time pathologists, to deliver to our customers the level of quality and support they deserve.\r\n成立于1994年，马凯细胞主要侧重于生产和销售用于诊断免疫组织化学（IHC）的抗体。我们的主要焦点是在体外诊断提供优质和创新的抗体，以进一步满足临床市场。马凯细胞通过全球国内的销售队伍，我们的技术顾问，以及国际经销商团队提供病理实验室和研究设施。我们鼓励智力成长的公司，这是我们的目标是留在我们行业当前问题的顶部，这样我们可以把我们的客户提供最新和最具创新性的抗体可用。\r\n此外，细胞马凯制造和供应的主要抗体本塔纳医疗系统（罗氏集团成员）是谁在自动化IHC平台的全球领导者。最后，我们是唯一的IHC公司，雇佣一队医生，其中两名专职病理学家，以提供给客户的质量和支持，帮助他们应有的水平之一。\r\n以上信息如有疏漏，请联系我们。\r\nQQ：3438957514\r\n电话：40004-91360','2016-05-09 19:04:32','0','2016-09-13 16:47:51',NULL,NULL,'99','0','~/UpLoadFiles/NavigationLogo/20160705152128.PNG',NULL,'~/UpLoadFiles/NavigationImage/20160705152137.PNG','0',NULL,NULL,'91360智慧病理网,91360智慧病理网网址导航,中国病理网址导航,病理网址导航,91360厂商,厂商动态,Cell Marque','Established in 1994, Cell Marque primarily focuses on producing and marketing antibodies for diagnostic immunohistochemistry (IHC). Our main focus is providing quality and innovative antibodies for in vitro diagnostic use to further serve the clinical market. Cell Marque serves pathology laboratories and research facilities globally through a domestic sales force, our team of Technical Consultants'), ('87','徕卡','http://www.leica-microsystems.com/home/','8','0','1',NULL,NULL,'40004-91360',NULL,NULL,'主办单位：徕卡显微系统(上海)贸易有限公司\r\n备案信息：沪ICP备14016987号-1(收录日期2016.7.6）\r\n网站简介：Leica Microsystems develops and manufactures microscopes and scientific instruments for the analysis of microstructures and nanostructures. Widely recognized for optical precision and innovative technology, the company is one of the market leaders in compound and stereo microscopy, digital microscopy, confocal laser scanning and super-resolution microscopy with related imaging systems, electron microscopy sample preparation, and surgical microscopy.\r\n以上信息如有疏漏，请联系我们。\r\nQQ：3438957514\r\n电话：40004-91360','2016-05-09 19:04:32','0','2016-09-13 14:58:19',NULL,NULL,'94','0','~/UpLoadFiles/NavigationLogo/20160705152641.PNG',NULL,'~/UpLoadFiles/NavigationImage/20160705152655.PNG','0',NULL,NULL,'91360智慧病理网,91360智慧病理网网址